# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository (prevents CRLF churn from
# Windows/WSL editors). Git auto-detects binary files and leaves them untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Be explicit about common binary types so they are never line-ending normalized.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.pdf  binary
